data.description: CONVENIENT LOCATION in X-FLOOD ZONE!!! This cute 3 Bedroom/1 Bathroom home is a perfect starter home, weekend getaway or investment property. Vaulted ceiling and large windows in the living area gives a light, bright and spacious feeling to this quaint home. Primary bedroom has plenty of closet space with 2 closets, including a huge walk-in closet! Located in an X flood zone, so no flood insurance is required. Walkable to restaurants, shopping & John Pennekamp State Park where you can launch your boat, jump on a diving, snorkeling or glassbottom boat trip out to the coral reef, kayak or canoe the mangrove trails, bike, hike, or just enjoy the visitor center and huge aquarium. The fenced & spacious backyard is perfect for pets and includes a patio & fire pit for entertaining, as well as a storage shed. Recent updates & modifications include: Tankless water heater, washer & dryer, computerized refrigerator, new bath and shower, new exterior siding, and plank tile flooring in the primary bedroom and walk-in closet.
